              <tooltip column='[federated.1x6bgsu1iy0eyn11mww7e11l2iig].[sum:units:qk]' />
            </encodings>
            <customized-tooltip>
              <formatted-text>
                <run fontcolor='#b9a313' fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='16' underline='true'>Dashboard Information Overview</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'>This dashboard presents a unified view of customer revenue within a hospitality environment by integrating booking and service data into a single source of truth.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'>Revenue is calculated as:</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#b9a313' fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'>• Stay Cost = Days Stayed × Room Day Rate  </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#b9a313' fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'>• Service Cost = Units × Service Rate  </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#b9a313' fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'>• Total Revenue = Stay Cost + Service Cost  </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'>A </run>
                <run fontcolor='#b9a313' fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'>20%</run>
                <run fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'> discount is applied to customers whose total bill exceeds</run>
                <run fontcolor='#b9a313' fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'> KES 50,000.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'>The data model follows a star schema design, ensuring consistent and reliable reporting across departments including bookings, rooms, services, and customer data.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontname='Trebuchet MS' fontsize='9'>Use filters to explore performance by customer, hotel, or service type. Visualizations highlight revenue contribution and discount eligibility.</run>
              </formatted-text>
            </customized-tooltip>
            <style>
              <style-rule element='mark'>
                <format attr='shape' value='Info Icon/Info Icon.png' />
                <format attr='mark-labels-cull' value='true' />
                <format attr='mark-labels-show' value='false' />
              </style-rule>
              <style-rule element='pane'>
